About This Company
Al-Khaleej Computers & Electronic Systems is a leading system integration and computer services company in the Arabian Gulf region.
The firm was established in 1979 by a group of five Saudi Arabian partners who were affiliated with the King Fahad University of Petroleum and Minerals.
From that begining,
Al-Khaleej has grown to prominence in the region's computer industry.
Our clients have included virtually every Saudi Arabian Government ministry and agency,
universities in Saudi Arbia, Kuwait and teh United Arab Emirates, and domestics and international private sector companies.
Al-Khaleej is the flag ship organization within the Al-Khaleej/Al-Falak group of companies, which includes:
Al-Falak Electronic Equipment & Supplies
Al-Khaleej Training & Electronic Industries
Shining Horizon Medical Company
Al-Khaleej is a professional information technology services company offering a skilled technical and administrative staff of more than two hundred and fifty multinational and multilingual specialists.
We have a reputation of being highly responsive to the needs of our clients.
Website: http://www.al-khaleej.net/
